9	// THE SAFETY CONTRACT (why this cannot fabricate a breach):
10	//   1. FILTER-ONLY, ENFORCED STRUCTURALLY. The returned findings array is built by mapping over the
11	//      INPUT candidates and stamping each one in place. It is NEVER built from the model's returned
12	//      verdicts. A verdict is consumed only via a Map lookup keyed by an id THIS module assigned to its
13	//      own candidate. A verdict for an id no input owns is never looked up; an invented finding cannot
14	//      exist in the output. Proven by p3-adjudicator-invented-finding.js: |output| == |input|, always.
