220	// applyVerdicts(batch, verdicts) - THE FILTER-ONLY CORE. Iterate the INPUT candidates and look up each
221	// one's verdict by the id THIS module assigned it. Nothing is ever created from `verdicts`; a verdict
222	// for an unknown id is simply never looked up. This is why an invented finding cannot be injected.
223	function applyVerdicts(batch, verdicts) {
224	  const byId = new Map();
